<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Rudrohom Mail</title>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		body{
			font-family: 'Poppins' !important;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div
		style="max-width: 800px; margin: 15px auto; border: 1px solid #fff; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;border:1px solid #666">
		<div style="padding: 20px 15px; text-align: center;">
			<img src="https://jusbid.in:1337/images/logo_jusbid.png" alt=""
				style="width:200px;height:100%;object-fit: contain;">
		</div>
		<div style="text-align: center">
			<h2 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;font-size: 2.2em;color:#000000">New Hotel {{hotel_name}} has been Added! </h2>
			<!-- <h4 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;color:#000000">{{createdAt}}</h4> -->
			<button style="background-color: #25D366;
			color: #ffffff;
			border-radius: 10px;
			border: none;
			padding: 10px 40px;">Let's Welcome {{hotel_name}}</button>
		</div>
		<div style="margin:30px 0px;">
			<img style="width:100%"
				src="https://www.transindiaholidays.com/Areas/Blog/UploadImages/Id_5c1a0aa3-7794-410a-952f-17ad8dc95c2c.jpg">
		</div>
		<div style="padding: 30px 15px; color: #333; font-size: 14px;">
			<div>
				<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
					<strong>{{name}}</strong>,
				</p>
			</div>

			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
				Dear BDM - <strong>{{name}}</strong>, <br>

                Jusbid would like to inform you that <strong>{{hotel_name}}</strong> is added by your BDE <strong>{{bde_name}}</strong> recently, let's welcome new hotel in our business, BDE and hotelier will be waiting for further instructions,

                Thank you for your prompt attention to the above, kindly check your hotel list to check updates,<br>

                Kind Regards,<br>
			</p>
			<p style="padding: 10px;text-align:center;">
				<a href="https://jusbid.in/admin/" target="_blank" style="background-color: #25D366;
					color: #ffffff;
					border-radius: 10px;
					border: none;
					padding: 10px 40px;">
					<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.8px;">Visit BDM Panel</span>
				</a>
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;">Thank you,</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;"><strong>Team Rudrohom.</strong></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>